'''強尼·維加斯'''（'''Johnny Vegas'''，{{bd|1970年|9月5日}}）是[[英國|英國]]的一位演員和喜劇演員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/lifestyle/nostalgia/johnny-vegas-lost-myself-johnny-3440413|title=Johnny Vegas: I lost myself in 'Johnny Vegas'|first=Paddy|last=Shennan|work=[[Liverpool_Echo|Liverpool Echo]]|date=30 November 2009|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2013-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219020912/http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/lifestyle/nostalgia/johnny-vegas-lost-myself-johnny-3440413|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他以憤怒的咆哮、超現實的幽默、臃腫的身材和高而沙啞的嗓音著稱<ref name="Johnny Vegas turns out for Saints">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/4229109.stm|title=Johnny Vegas turns out for Saints|work=BBC News|date=3 February 2005|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2017-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910180421/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/england/merseyside/4229109.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Heaton">{{cite web|last=Heaton|first=Paul|title=@paulheatonsolo|url=https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7431/13572098834_89a4e2170f_o.jpg|accessdate=2 April 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181001204246/https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7431/13572098834_89a4e2170f_o.jpg|archive-date=2018-10-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。維加斯的主要作品包括BBC喜劇Ideal和ITV喜劇Benidorm。
